{"tid":990082,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(童年玩具)有冇人記得細個玩既鬥車?","createTime":"2019-01-21T10:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T15:51:50.000Z","uid":119688,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f961c6cbcfa91e99ccb322bb6fae71568604be7a","tid":990082,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"印象中都係因為卡通片而紅<br />\n但紅左一陣就無人玩<br />\n所以未必多人清楚<br />\n鬥車係玩撞尻人<br />\n車身係會旋轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n360度都可以用黎攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daN2Jwv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaN2Jwv.jpg&h=cd9b8060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突然勾返起個回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前有部勁快 放係屋企玩<br />\n因為部車係無定向 <br />\n會自轉又會撞黎撞去<br />\n比佢車親手指腳指無數次<br />\n試過車親我老母比佢一巴車落黎<br />\n仲要跪神主檯 塊面由下午紅到天黑都未散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭先上youtube睇原來印度賓賓<br />\n好興玩 又幾刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5_isBi1yrN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5_isBi1yrN8&d=D%2FmRimXGJcBjWi6znu1V60%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=cc2453f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5_isBi1yrN8</a>"},{"pid":"817490db0af424bba5adc25f68a1b6839d88c15e","tid":990082,"uid":119688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"好想搞到車會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ed2